text: Kalyan Krishna Kurasala is an Indian film screenwriter and director known for his works primarily in Telugu cinema. In 2016, he directed Soggade Chinni Nayana. In 2017, he directed Rarandoi Veduka Chudham produced by Annapurna Studios.In 2018, he directed Nela Ticket. == Filmography == {| class="wikitable sortable" !Year !Title !Notes |- |2016 |Soggade Chinni Nayana |Debut in Telugu cinema |- |2017 |Rarandoi Veduka Chudham | |- |- |2018 |Nela Ticket | |} == References == == External links== * Category:Indian film directors Category:Indian people Category:Living people Category:Telugu film directors Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
